          Driven by passion, I‚Äôm currently finalizing my homelab setup and
          starting to dive deeper into cybersecurity. I also enjoy helping
          others and sharing resources, mainly through writing blog posts to
          give back the knowledge the community has shared with me.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech Stack Grid -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">
            Tech Stack & Tools
          </h3>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Infrastructure -->
          <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-slate-300">
            <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-100">
                <span class="text-2xl">üèóÔ∏è</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">
                Infrastructure
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">NixOS</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Fedora CoreOS</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Ansible</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Terraform</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Nix</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Containers -->
          <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-slate-300">
            <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-100">
                <span class="text-2xl">üì¶</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">
                Containers & CI/CD
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Docker</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Podman</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">CI/CD</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Networking -->
